{"word":"G3939 - παροικέω - paroikéō - par-oy-keh'-o - Sojourn in","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παροικέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">paroikéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">par-oy-keh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Sojourn in</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அந்நியராயிரு"},{"paragraph":"1. properly, to dwell beside (one) or in one's neighborhood"},{"paragraph":"2. in the Scriptures to be or dwell in a place as a stranger, to sojourn"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3844 - παρά - pará - par-ah'/3844\">G3844</a> and <a href=\"#/G3611 - οἰκέω - oikéō - oy-keh'-o/3611\">G3611</a>; to <i>dwell near</i>, that is, <i>reside</i> as a <i>foreigner:</i> - sojourn in, be a stranger.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3939/3939\">G3939</a>, <a href=\"#/G3940/3940\">G3940</a>, <a href=\"#/G3941/3941\">G3941</a>"}]}